params.description: Output only . The resource ID of the annotation spec that this annotation pertains to. The annotation spec comes from either an ancestor dataset, or the dataset that was used to train the model in use.

params.description: Output only. The value of [AnnotationSpec.display_name][google.cloud.automl.v1beta1.AnnotationSpec.display_name] when the model was trained.
